OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779127867
OL,3,CDirect rail service between Oxford and
OL,4,CBristol starts after 23 years
OL,6,FDirect train services linking Oxford,
OL,7,FSwindon and Bristol have started again
OL,8,Ffor the first time in more than 20
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FGreat Western Railway (GWR) services
OL,12,Fwill run Monday to Saturday, calling
OL,13,Fat Bristol Temple Meads, Bath Spa,
OL,14,FChippenham, Swindon and Oxford.
OL,16,FThe last direct services between
OL,17,FOxford and Bristol had previously run
OL,18,Fin 2003.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
