CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779127867
OL,3,CDirect rail service between Oxford and
OL,4,CBristol starts after 23 years
OL,6,FIt means passengers can now travel
OL,7,Fbetween Oxford and Bristol in just
OL,8,Fover one hour and ten minutes.
OL,10,FGWR said it had worked closely with
OL,11,FNetwork Rail to ensure services can be
OL,12,Frestored as part of the railway's May
OL,13,Ftimetable change.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
