PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779127867
OL,3,CDirect rail service between Oxford and
OL,4,CBristol starts after 23 years
OL,6,FLocal politicians, including Swindon
OL,7,FSouth MP Heidi Alexander, have praised
OL,8,Fthe opening of the service.
OL,10,FMs Alexander said it was "great news",
OL,11,Fadding that "stronger transport links
OL,12,Fare vital to unlocking opportunity".
OL,14,FGWR Managing Director Mark Hopwood
OL,15,FCBE, meanwhile, hailed the new direct
OL,16,Fservices as "transformational".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
