CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779127867
OL,3,CDirect rail service between Oxford and
OL,4,CBristol starts after 23 years
OL,6,FHe said: "We know this is something
OL,7,Fcustomers and partners have been
OL,8,Fcampaigning for over recent years, and
OL,9,Fwe're very grateful to those who have
OL,10,Fsupported our case to make this happen.
OL,12,F"The economic and social benefits are
OL,13,Fclear, and we are confident that these
OL,14,Fnew services demonstrate the value of
OL,15,Frail in driving economic growth,
OL,16,Fenvironmental benefits, and creating
OL,17,Feducation and employment opportunities
OL,18,Fwhich previously were not possible -
OL,19,Fas well as directly linking two of the
OL,20,Fkey leisure markets in the UK."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
